#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This release fixes [[known security vulnerabilities|security/"
"known_security_vulnerabilities_in_4.14]]. You should upgrade as soon as "
"possible."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!toc levels=1]]\n"
msgstr "[[!toc levels=1]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h1 id=\"features\">New features</h1>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Add a **Don't Show Again** button to the security notification when starting "
"Tails in a virtual machine."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h1 id=\"changes\">Changes and updates</h1>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Update *Tor Browser* to [10.0.9](https://blog.torproject.org/new-release-"
"tor-browser-1009)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Update *Thunderbird* to [78.6.0](https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/"
"thunderbird/78.6.0/releasenotes/)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Update *Linux* to 5.9.15. This should improve the support for newer hardware "
"(graphics, Wi-Fi, etc.)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h1 id=\"fixes\">Fixed problems</h1>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Fix support for the Ledger hardware wallets in *Electrum*.  ([[!tails_ticket "
"18080]])"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Fix sharing mobile data, also called *USB tethering*, on iOS 14 or later.  "
"([[!tails_ticket 18097]])"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Clarify the error message when starting from a USB stick that is too small.  "
"([[!tails_ticket 18073]])"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"For more details, read our [[!tails_gitweb debian/changelog desc=\"changelog"
"\"]]."
msgstr ""
"Lesen Sie für mehr Details unser [[!tails_gitweb debian/changelog desc="
"\"Änderungsprotokoll\"]]."

